src:
Gewaltige Wasserfontäne schiesst aus Hochhaus
Minutenlang sprudelte am Sonntag in der US-Stadt Philadelphia eine grosse Menge Wasser aus einem 61-stöckigen Wolkenkratzer.
04 Nov 2019, 21:54 by mp
text:
Huge water fountain shoots from skyscraper
For a few minutes on Sunday in the US city of Philadelphia, a large amount of water gushed from a 61-story skyscraper.
04 Nov 2019, 21:54 by mp
